  ----
  ((X>>C2) ^ ((C1 >> C2)^C3))[i]
  = (X>>C2)[i] ^ (C1 >> C2)^C3)[i] [bit-of-xor]
  # NOTE: negative entries will be 0 because it is LOGICAL shift right
  = X[i - C2]₀ ^ ((C1 >> C2)[i] ^ C3[i]) [bit-of-lshr]
  = X[i - C2]₀ ^ (C1[i-C2] ^ C3[i]) [bit-of-lshr]
-/
